name: .NET Framework
description: .NET Framework 4.8 is the latest release and will continue to be supported while running on a supporting version of Windows (Windows 11). Framework will be replaced by .NET

name: .NET Core
description: .NET Core 3.5 is slated for EOS on 12/31/22

name: .NET
description: .NET 6 is the latest LTS and should be considered for new development

name: AccessIndiana
description: SSO and Auth/Authorization/Access solution developed and maintained by Indiana State Enterprise. Should be considered as a low cost alternative to TID if price is a driver in the decision making process. TID should still be the first option to concider.

name: Google Universal Analytics
description: Google Universal Analytics is approaching end of life. Google Analytics 4 should be considered as alternative when looking at implementing this functionality

name: MSP Auth Service
description: NIC Micro Service Platform developed and maintained by the NIC CTO Group. Consist of a nuber of micro services used across the organization. Using MSP for Auth/Authorization/Access is not recommended at this time and TID should be considered as an alternative when needing to implement an Auth/Authorization/Access solution.

name: NIC CDB
description: NIC CDB is billing and payment scheduling component of the NIC Payment ecosystem. Although NIC CDB could be used for Auth/Authorization/Access it is not intended as an Auth/Authorization/Access solution and should be replaced when used for that purpose. Using CDB for Auth/Authorization/Access has the potential to impact PCI scope for applications.

name: TID-C
description: Single sign on solution developed by Tyler and based on Okta. TID-C is intended to be used for citizen IDs.

name: TID-W
description: Single sign on solution developed by Tyler and based on Okta. TID-W is intended to be used for agency user IDs.

name: Tyler Assurance
description: Tyler Assurance is a Test Automation Platform that specializes in UI Test Automation. Our solution consists of our Automation Framework, Test Results Website, and our online training. https://confl.tylertech.com/display/TylerAssurance/Tyler+Assurance

name: Tyler Forge
description: RAI design and development framework. Tyler developed and maintained. Built around Tyler branding and standardization
